hadiths[49]{hadithnumber,text}:
6723,"main bimar padaa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laaey, donon hazraat paidal chal kar aaey they. donon hazraat jab aaey to mujh par ghashii taarii thi, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur wuzu ka pani mere uper chhidkaa mujhey hosh hua to maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! apne maal ki (taqseem) kis tarah karun? ya apne maal ka kis tarah faisla karun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey koi jawab nahi diya, yahan tak ke meeraas ki aayatein nazil huin."
6724,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaayaa  ''bad-gumaanii se bachtey raho, kyonke guman (bad-gumaanii) sabse jhooti baat hai. aapas mein aik doosrey ki burai ki talash mein na lagey raho na aik doosrey se bughz rakho aur na peeth peechhey kisi ki burai karo, balke Allah ke bandey bhaaii-bhaaii bin kar raho.''"
6725,"Fatima aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se apni meeraas ka mutalba karne aaey, ye fidak ki zameen ka mutalba kar rahe they aur khaibar mein bhi apne hissey kaa."
6726,"hamara koi waaris nahi hota jo kuchh ham chhodein wo sab sadqa hai, bila shubah aale-Muhammad usi maal mein se apna kharch pura karegi Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! main koi aisi baat nahi honey doonga , balke jisey maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kartey dekha hoga wo main bhi karunga . bayan kya ke is par Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne unse talluq kaat liya aur maut tak unse kalam nahi kya."
6727,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaayaa  ''hamaarii wiraasat nahi hoti ham jo kuchh bhi chhodein wo sadqa hai.''
6728,"Muhammad-bin-jubair-bin-mut'im ne mujh se Maalik-bin-aous ki us hadis ka aik hissey zikr kya tha. phir main khud Maalik-bin-aous ke paas gaya aur unse ye hadis poochhi to unhon-ne bayan kya ke main umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua phir unke haajib yarfa'a ne ja kar unse kaha ke Usmaan, Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Zubair aur Sad aap ke paas aana chahtey hain? unhon-ne kaha ke achchha aaney do. chunanche unhein andar aaney ki ijazat de di. phir kaha, kya aap Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi aaney ki ijazat dengey? kaha ke haan, aaney do. chunanche Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ameerul-momineen mere aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmyan faisla kar dijiye. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main tumhen Allah ki qism deta hun jiske hukm se aasman w zameen qaaim hain kya tumhen malum hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke hamari wiraasat taqseem nahi hoti jo kuchh ham chhodein wo sab raahey Allah sadqa hai? us se murad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khud apni hi zaat thi. jumla haaziriin boley ke ji haan, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye irshad farmaya tha. phir Umar, Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur poochha, kya tumhen malum hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha? unhon-ne bhi tasdeeq ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye irshad farmaya tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya phir main ab aap logon se is maamle mein guftgu karunga . Allah Taala ne is fay (فے) ke mamla main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye kuchh hissey makhsoos kar diye jo aap ke siwa kisi aur ko nahi milta tha. chunanche Allah Taala ne farmaya tha (ما أفاء الله على رسوله) se  قدير tak. ye to khas Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hissa tha. Allah ki qism ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey tumharey liye hi makhsoos kya tha aur tumharey siwa kisi ko is par tarjeeh nahi di thi, tumhen ko usmein se detey they aur taqseem kartey they. aakhir usmein se ye maal baqi reh gaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein se apne ghar walon ke liye saal bhar ka kharcha letey they, iske baad jo kuchh baqi bachta usey un kharch mein kharch kartey jo Allah kne muqarrar kiya hua hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye tarze amal aap ki zindagi bhar raha. mein aapko Allah ki qism de kar kehta hun, kya aap logon ko malum hai? logon ne kaha ke ji haan. phir aap ne Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, main Allah ki qism de kar poochhta hun kya aap logon ko ye malum hai? unhon-ne bhi kaha ke ji haan. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ab main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka naaib hun chunanche unhon-ne is par qabze mein rakh kar us tarze amal ko jari rakha jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka usmein tha. Allah Taala ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi wafat di to maine kaha ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke naaib ka naaib hun. mein bhi do saal se is par qaabiz hon aur us maal mein wahi karta hun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kya. phir aap donon mere paas aaey ho. aap donon ki baat aik hai aur mamla bhi aik hi hai. aap (Abbaas (rz)) mere paas apne bhatijey ki meeraas se apna hissey leney aaey ho aur aap ( Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) apni biwi ka hissa leney aaey ho jo unke walid ki taraf se unhein milta . main kehta hun ke agar aap donon chahtey hain to main usey aapko de sakta hun lekin aap log iske siwa koi aur faisla chahtey hain to us zaat ki qism jiske hukm se aasman w zameen qaaim hain, main us maal mein iske siwa aur koi faisla nahi kar sakta, qiyamat tak, agar aap iske mutabiq amal nahi kar saktey to wo jaaidaad mujhey wapas kar dijiye main iska bhi bando-bast kar loonga."
6729,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaayaa  ''meri wiraaset Dinar ki shakl mein taqseem nahi hogi. maine apni beeviyon ke kharchey aur apne aamilon ki ujrat ke baad jo kuchh chhoda hai wo sab sadqa hai.''
6730,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to aap ki beeviyon ne chaha ke Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bhejiin, apni meeraas talab karne ke liye. phir Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne yad dilaayaa. kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nahi farmaya tha ke hamari wiraasat taqseem nahi hoti, ham jo kuchh chhod jayen wo sab sadqa hai?"
6731,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main mominon ka khud unse zyada haqdaar hun. isliye unmein se jo koi qarz daar marey ga aur adaaeygi ke liye kuchh na chhodey ga to ham par uski adaaeygi ki zimme-dari hai aur jisne koi maal chhoda hoga wo uskey waarison ka hissa hai.''
6732,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meeraas iske haq daaron tak pahuncha 2 aur jo kuchh baqi bachchey wo sabse zyada qaribi mard azeez ka hissa hai.''
6733,"main Makka Mukarrama mein (hijjatul-wadaa mein) bimar pad gaya aur maut ke qareeb pahunch gaya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laey to maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mere paas bahut zyada maal hai aur aik ladki ke siwa iska koi waaris nahi to kya mujhey apne maal ke do tehai hissey ka sadqa kar dena chaahiye? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. bayan kya ke maine arz kya phir aadhey ka kar dun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. maine arz kya aik tehai kaa? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan. mano tehai bhi bahut hai, agar tum apne bachchon ko maaldaar chhodo to ye us se behtar hai ke unhein tangdast chhodo aur wo logon ke samney hath phailaatey phirein aur tum jo bhi kharch karogey is par tumhen sawab milega yahan tak ke us luqmey par bhi sawab milega jo tum apni biwi ke munh mein rakho gey . phir maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya main apni hijrat mein peechhey reh jaaunga ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar mere baad tum peechhey reh bhi gaey tab bhi jo amal tum karogey aur us se Allah ki khushnoodii maqsud hogi to iske zariey darja aur martaba buland hoga aur ghaaliban tum mere baad zinda rahogey aur tum se bahut se logon ko fayda hoga aur bahuton ko nuqsan pahunchega . qaabiley afsos to Sad ibne- Khaula hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke barey mein isliye afsos ka izhar kya ke (hijrat ke baad ittifaq se) unki wafat Makka Mukarrama mein hi ho gaee. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke Sad ibne- Khaula (Raziallahu anhu) bani Aamir-bin-Luii ke aik aadmi they."
6734,Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey yahan Yaman mein muallim aur ameer bin kar tashrif laey. ham ne unse aik aisey shakhs ke wiraaset ke barey mein puchha jiski wafat hui ho aur us ne aik beti aur aik behan chhodi ho aur us ne apni beti ko aadha aur behan ko bhi aadha diya ho.
6735,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' pahley meeraas unke waarison tak pahuncha do aur jo baqi reh jaey wo usko milega jo mard maiyat ka bahut nazdiikii (نزدیکی) rishtedar ho.''
6736,"abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se beti , pottii (پوتی) aur behan ki meeraas ke barey mein puchha gaya to unhon-ne kaha ke beti ko aadha milega aur behan ko aadha milega aur to ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan jaa, shayad wo bhi yahi bataein gey. phir ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya aur abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat bhi pahunchai gaee to unhon-ne kaha ke main agar aisa fatwa dun to gumrah ho chuka aur theek rastey se bhatak gaya. main to usmein wahi faisla karunga jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha ke beti ko aadha milega,  pottii (پوتی) ko  chathaa (چھٹا) hissey milega , is tarah do tehai poori ho jaeygi aur phir jo baqi bachchey ga wo behan ko milega. phir abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat un tak pahunchai to unhon-ne kaha ke jab tak ye aalim tum mein maujood hain mujh se masayel na puchha karo."
6737,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' meeraas uske haqdaar tak pahuncha do aur jo baqi reh jaey wo sabse qareeb waley mard ko de do.''
6738,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo ye farmaya hai ke agar main is ummat ke kisi aadmi ko khaleel banata to unko (abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko) ko khaleel banaataa, lekin Islam ka talluq hi sabse behtar hai to usmein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dada ko bap ke darje mein rakha hai."
6739,pahley maal ki aulad mustahiq thi aur waalidain ko wasiiyat ka haq tha. phir Allah Taala ne usmein se jo chaha mansukh kar diya aur ladkon ko ladkiyon ke dugnaa haq diya aur waalidain ko aur unmein se har aik ko chhatey hissey ka mustahiq qarar diya aur biwi ko aathwein aur chauthey hissey ka haq daar qarar diya aur shauhar ko aadhey ya chothai ka haqdaar qarar diya.
6740,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bani Lahyaan ki aik aurat  maliiyaa (ملیا) binte Uwemir ke bachchey ke barey mein jo aik aurat ki mar se murda paida hua tha ke maarney wali aurat ko khoon baha ke taur par aik ghulam ya londi ada karne ka hukm farmaya tha. phir wo aurat bachcha giraaney wali jiske mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne faisla diya tha mar gaee to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne faisla kya ke uski meeraas iske ladkon aur shauhar ko de di jaey aur ye diyat ada karne ka hukm iske kunba walon ko diya tha.
6741,Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein hamarey darmyan ye faisla kya tha ke aadha beti ko milega aur aadha behan ko . phir Sulaiman ne jo us hadis ko riwayat kya to itna hi kaha ke Muaz ne ham kunba walon ko ye hukm diya tha ye nahi kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein.
6742,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke faisla ke mutabiq uska faisla karunga, ladki ko aadhaa, pottii (پوتی) ko chathaa (چھٹا) aur jo baqi bachchey behan ka hissa hai."
6743,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere ghar tashrif laey aur main bimar tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani mangwaya aur wuzu kya, phir apne wuzu ke pani se mujh par chhinta daala to mujhey hosh aa gaya. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! meri bahnein hain? is par meeraas ki aayat nazil hui."
6744,"aakhiri aayat ( meeraas ki) sura Nisa ke aakhir ki aayatein nazil huin ( يستفتونك قل الله يفتيكم في الكلالة‏ (ke '' aap se fatwa poochhtey hain, keh dijiye ke Allah Taala tumhen kalaala ke barey mein fatwa deta hai.''"
6745,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main musalmanon ka khud unki zaat se bhi zyada wali hun. to jo shakhs mar jaey aur maal chhod jaey to wo iske waarison ka haq hai aur jisne biwi bachchey chhodey hon ya qarz ho, to main unka wali hon, unke liye mujh se maanga jaaey.''"
6746,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meeraas iske waarison tak pahuncha do aur jo kuchh usmein se bach rahe wo qaribi azeez mard ka haq hai.''
6747,"aur unse Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( ولكل جعلنا موالي‏ ) aur ( والذين عقدت أيمانكم‏ ) ke mutaalliq batlaya ke muhajireen jab Madina aaey to ذوی الارحام ke ilawa Ansar w muhajireen bhi aik doosrey ki wiraasat patey they. us bhaaii-chaargii ki wjah se jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke darmyan karaai thi, phir jab aayat ( جعلنا موالي‏) nazil hui to farmaya ke usne ( والذين عقدت أيمانكم‏) ko mansukh kar diya."
6748,aik shakhs ne apni biwi se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein liaan kya aur uske bachche ko apna bachcha manney se inkar kar diya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon ke darmyan judai kara di aur bachcha aurat ko de diya.
6749,"Utba apne bhai Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ko wasiiyat kar gaya tha ke Zam-aa ki kaneez ka ladka mera hai aur usey apni parwarish mein ley lenaa. fateh Makka ke saal Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey lena chaha aur kaha ke mere bhai ka ladka hai aur us ne mujhey iske barey mein wasiiyat ki thi. is par abd-bin-Zam'a (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur kaha ke ye mera bhai hai aur mere bap ki londi ka ladka hai, iske bistar par paida hua hai. aakhir ye donon ye mamla Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas le gaey to Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! ye mere bhai ka ladka hai us ne iske barey mein mujhey wasiiyat ki thi. abd-bin-Zam'a ne kaha ke ye mera bhai hai, mere bap ki baandi ka ladka aur bap ke bistar par paida hua hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, abd-bin-Zam'a ! ye tumharey paas rahega , ladka bistar ka haq hai aur zaanii ke hisse mein patthar hain. phir Sauda-binte-Zama (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke us ladkey se parda kya kar kyonke Utba ke sath uski shabaahat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekh li thi. chunanche phir us ladkey ne Ummul-Momenin ko apni wafat tak nahi dekha."
6750,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' ladka bistar waley ka haq hota hai.''
6751,"maine Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko khareednaa chaha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein khareed ley , 'walaa' to iske sath qaaim hoti hai jo aazad kar de aur Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko aik bakri mili to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye unke liye sadqa thi lekin hamarey liye hadiya hai. hakam ne bayan kya ke unke shauhar aazad they. hakam ka qaul mursal manqul hai. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine unhein ghulam dekha tha."
6752,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' 'walaa' usi ke sath qaaim hoti hai jo aazad kar de. ''
6753,Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya musalman saayeba nahi banatey aur daure-jaahiliyat mein mushrekeen saayeba banatey they.
6754,"ya Rasulullah ! maine aazad karne ke liye Barira ko khareednaa chaha lekin unke maalikon ne apne liye unki 'walaa' ki shart laga di hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein aazad kar de, 'walaa' to aazad karne waley ke sath qaaim hoti hai. bayan kya ke phir maine unhein khareedaa aur aazad kar diya aur maine Barira ko ikhtiyar diya (ke chaahein to shauhar ke sath reh sakti hain warna alehda bhi ho sakti hain) to unhon-ne shauhar se alehadgii ko pasand kya aur kaha ke mujhey itna itnaa maal bhi diya jaey to main pahley shauhar ke sath nahi rahoon gii . Aswad ne bayan kya ke unke shauhar aazad they. Aswad ka qaul munqata' hai aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaul sahi hai ke maine unhein ghulam dekha."
6755,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke hamarey paas koi kitab nahi hai jisey ham padhein, siwa Allah ki kitab Quran ke aur uske ilawa ye saheefa bhi hai. bayan kya ke phir wo saheefa nikala to usmein zakhmon (ke qisaas (aur oonton ki zakat ke masayel they. rawi ne bayan kya ke usmein ye bhi tha ke eir se Saur tak Madina haram hai jisne is Deen mein koi nai baat paida ki ya nai baat karne waley ko panah di to is par Allah aur farishton aur insanon sab ki laanat hai aur qiyamat ke din uska koi nek amal maqbool na hoga aur jisne apne maalikon ki ijazat ke baghair doosrey logon se mawaalaat qaaim kar li to is par farishton aur insanon sab ki laanat hai, qiyamat ke din uska koi nek amal maqbool na hoga aur musalmanon ka zimma ( qaul w qarar , kisi ko panah dena wghaira) aik hai. aik adnaa musalman ke panah dene ko bhi qaaim rakhney ki koshish ki jaeygi. to jisne kisi musalman ki di hui panah ko todaa , is par Allah ki, farishton aur insanon sab ki laanat hai qiyamat ke din uska koi nek amal qabool nahi kya jaeyga"
6756,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 'walaa' ke talluq ko bechney , usko hiba karne se mana farmaya hai."
6757,"Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne aik kaneez ko aazad karne ke liye khareednaa chaha to kaneez ke maalikon ne kaha ke ham bech saktey hain lekin 'walaa' hamarey sath hogi. Ummul-Momenin ne iska zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us shart ko rukawat na banney do, 'walaa' hamesha usi ke sath qaaim hoti hai jo aazad kare."
6758,"maine Barira ko khareednaa chaha to unke maalikon ne shart lagai ke 'walaa' unke sath qaaim hogi. maine iska tazkira Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein aazad kar do, 'walaa' qeemat ada karne waley hi ke sath qaaim hoti hai. bayan kya ke phir maine aazad kar diya. phir unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bulaya aur unke shauhar ke maamle mein ikhtiyar diya. unhon-ne kaha ke agar mujhey ye ye cheezein bhi wo dedey to main iske sath raat guzarney ke liye taiyaar nahi. chunanche us ne shauhar se alehadgii ko pasand kya."
6759,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko khareednaa chaha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke ye log 'walaa' ki shart lagaatey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khareed lo, 'walaa' to usi ke sath qaaim hoti hai jo aazad karey ( aazad kiraaey ( ."
6760,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke 'walaa' uske sath qaaim hogi jo qeemat de aur ehsan karey (aazaad karke (
6761,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi gharaaney ka ghulam usi ka aik fard hota hai'' (ya isi tarah kuchh kaha).
6762,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi gharaaney ka bhanja iska aik fard hai.'' ( منهم‏ Mina . Mina (ya ( من أنفسهم (ke alfaz farmaai ( .
6763,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne maal chhoda (apni maut ke baad) wo iske waarison ka hai aur jisne qarz chhoda hai wo hamarey zimme hai.''
6764,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' musalman bap kaafir betey ka waaris nahi hota aur na kaafir betaa musalman bap kaa. ''
6765,"Sad-bin-abi-Waqas aur abd-bin-Zam'a (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik ladkey ke barey mein jhagdaa hua. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! ye mere bhai Utba-bin- abii-waqaas ka ladka hai, usne mujhey wasiiyat ki thi ke ye iska ladka hai aap uski mushabihat (similarity) usmein dekhiye aur abd-bin-Zam'a ne kaha ke mera bhai hai ya Rasulullah! mere walid ke bistar par unki londi se paida hua hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ladkey ki sura dekhi to uski Utba ke sath saaf mushabihat (similarity) waazeh thi, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, abd! ladka bistar waley ka hota hai aur zaanii ke hisse mein patthar hain aur aey Sauda-bint-Zam'a! (ummul-momeneen (Raziallahu anhu)) us ladkey se parda kya kar chunanche phir us ladkey ne Ummul-Momenin ko nahi dekha."
6766,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne apne bap ke siwa kisi aur ke betey honey ka dawa kya ye jantey huey ke wo iska bap nahi hai to jannat is par haram hai.
6767,is hadis ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mere donon kanon ne bhi suna hai aur mere dil ne usko mehfooz rakha hai.
6768,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''apne bap ka koi inkar na karey kyonke jo apne bap se munh modtaa hai (aur apne ko doosrey ka betaa zahir karta hai to) ye kufr hai.''
6769,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''2 auratein thin aur unke sath unke 2 bachchey bhi they, phir bhediyaa aaya aur aik bachchey ko utha kar ley gaya us ne apni sathi aurat se kaha ke bhediyaa terey bachchey ko ley gaya hai, dusri aurat ne kaha ke wo to tera bachcha ley gaya hai. wo donon auratein apna muqaddima Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke paas laaein to aap ne faisla badi ke haq mein kar diya. wo donon nikal kar Sulaimaan-bin-Daawood (Alaihissalam) ke paas gain aur unhein waaqie ki itlaa di. Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke chhuri lao mein ladkey ke 2 tukdey karke donon ko eik-eik doonga . is par chhoti aurat bol uthi ke aisa na kijiye aap par Allah raham karey, ye badi hi ka ladka hai lekin aap (Alaihissalam) ne faisla chhoti aurat ke haq mein kya. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! maine ( سكين ( chhuri ka lafz sabse pehli martaba (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban se) us din suna tha aur ham uske liye (apne qabila mein) ( مدية‏ (ka lafz boltey they."
6770,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan aik martaba bahut khush khosh tashrif laey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra chamak raha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum ne nahi dekha, Mujazzaz (eik qiyaafa shanaas) ne abhi abhii Zaid-bin-Haarisa aur Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke (sirf paon dekhey) aur kaha ke ye paon aik doosrey se talluq rakhtey hain.''"
6771,"aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut khush they aur farmaya '' Aaisha ! tum ne dekha nahi, Mujazzaz Mudliji aaya aur us ne Usama aur Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, donon ke jism par aik chadar thi, jisne donon ke saron ko dhak liya tha aur unke sirf paon khuley huey they, to usne kaha ke ye paon aik doosrey se talluq rakhtey hain.''"
